snippet.textDisplay:
Alright so I might be reading too deep into this but-

After listening to crowded room by selena gomez and then party monster I have come to the conclusion that this song was made by abel about him meeting selena gomez. In the lyrics he talks about a crowded room and seeing her. Talking about how he had to talk to her etc. In Selena's song crowded room, she talks about how a guy comes up to her to break the ice through the crowded room. Abel explains why he talked to her in the first place in after hours, saying how he was alone in the room and he wanted to distract himself. Basically saying," I was bored and I saw you. You were interesting to me and I wanted you. I shouldn't have done that but I did, if you give me another chance I will treat you right." Because we have to remember abel loved selena a lot.


With that said I think abel and selena first met in person, in a club. There they hooked up and then they built off of that to build their relationship. Selena wasn't over justin though and abel lowkey used her to get through thing, but as time went on he definitely began to feel more for her. Before he could really build more of it, when he had his Hopes up something happened and they ended their relationship.
